title: Multi-model query helper and diagnosis phase
---
Implement query_model helper wrapping Provider.complete with explicit model override. Implement Phase 1 (Diagnosis): parallel query of primary models (anthropic:claude-opus-4-6, openai-codex:gpt-5.4) via Lwt.all, fallback to secondary models (zai_coding:glm-5, kimi_coding:kimi-for-code) on failure, non-fatal error handling (continue with available results), diagnosis merging for fallback models. Deadlock-specific handling: when errors suggest deadlock (mutex timeout, Lwt_mutex, process hang, stale PID), always use powerful thinking models, include instructions to investigate locks/mutexes. AC: Queries 2 models in parallel. Falls back when primary fails. Merges fallback results. All-fail writes minimal report and exits cycle non-fatally.